Detailed Description

Equals the spirit:bank element in IP-Xact specification.

Bank represents a collection of address blocks, banks or subspace maps. Bank is a generalization of a class MemoryMapItem which is the base class also for classes AddressBlock and SubspaceMap.

void Bank::setItems ( QList< QSharedPointer< MemoryMapItem > > &  items  ) 

Set the items stored in the bank.

Calling this function deletes the old items stored in the bank. To keep old values function getItems() must be called to add the old values to the QList given as a parameter for this function.
